item.title: Soulsplit donater how to get rid f donate items
item.dc:creator: @xd_own3d_xd xd own3d xd
item.description:
@xd_own3d_xd wrote:

search for a partyhat id in your client.java file, eg red partyhat: 1038

so search for 1038 in your client.java and you will find something like this

if(wearID == 1038 && (donator != 1)) {
sM(“You Need To Be A Donator To Wear This Item.”);
return false;
}

simply delete it

Hope i helped
